Hello Everyone,

I am writing from <http://WPXStudios.com|WPXStudios.com>! We're excited to offer a *20%* partnership opportunity.

We are a web development company specializing in turning designs into fully functional dynamic websites using CMS like HubSpot, Shopify & WordPress or Laravel coded from scratch.

We are looking to partner with designers like you. As you design websites for your clients, we can develop them as your web development partner.

Once you complete the design, so you refer the client to us for development. We will close the deal with them, and everything will be transparent with you. You will get a *20% commission* on the actual project amount.

If you are interested, you can fill out the form below, and we'll reach out to you and schedule a meeting with you soon.

*Form:* <https://forms.gle/bnBAFPcFe4GYKQDp6>

Thanks
